title: 820-4924-A no turn on, liquid damage
message:
" PPBUS_G3H: 3.75v
------------
27: 0.71v"
Are you sure?
PPBUS_G3H requires R7120 voltage!

Check all components surrounding U7100.
Also check solders and traces.
You may need to change U7100 and Q7130.
